      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-B-00002-000-00043-V"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Austria</rs></addrLine><addrLine>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><foreign xml:lang="en"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Vienna</rs></foreign></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-B-00002-000-00043-R"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps">No. 36 – <rs type="place" ref="#pmb143734">Karnak. Ptolomey Gateways and the Temple of Khonsu, God
                        of the Moon</rs></hi>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00089-B-00002-000-00043-V"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb923">Assuan</rs>, <date when="1924-03-01">1. III</date></dateline></opener><p>Es ist halt doch sehr schön, schon um diese Zeit 30° Hitze zu haben – aber leben
               möchte man hier trotzdem nicht. Herzliche Grüße, auch an <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12692">Heini</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb3233">Lilli</rs>.
               <lb/>Ihr <lb/><signed>Felix Salten</signed></p></div>
      </body>
